<item>
            <title>[MNG-2254] the encoding parameter in xml declaration of POM is ignored </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MNG-2254</link>
                <project id="12316922" key="MNG">Maven (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;DefaultMavenProjectBuilder reads POM in system default character encoding, and the encoding parameter in xml declartion is ignored.&lt;br/&gt;
to fix this problem, We should&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;alternate&quot; type=&quot;square&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;fix  modello-plugin-xpp3 to use the xml parser which is able to handle the encoding parameter properly&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;regenerate maven-model using fixed modello-plugin-xpp3&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;fix DefaultMavenProjectBuilder to use regenerated maven-model properly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
